ISLAMABAD, Apr 01 (APP): Minister for Information and Broadcasting Chaudhry Fawad Hussain said on Friday that Prime Minister Imran Khan’s security has been beefed after the security agencies reported a plot to assassinate the prime minister.
Chaudhry Fawad said using his twitter handle, the government has taken this decision in the light of these reports.
